body:
As a support main, I hear this every 2nd game lobby:

&quot;Hey support, can you play blitz?&quot;

&quot;Hey support do you have Leona??&quot;

Hey support, can you play x y z.. 

I rarely hear any other role being told what champion to play, no where near as much as support. Why do people feel like they can tell support who to play? Why is support different from all other positions? does anyone else get this?
